{"tid":2491602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"匈牙利傳出手阻歐盟 　就香港事務發聲明批評中國","createTime":"2021-04-16T12:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T13:07:10.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e1c7432a06c11c7238c62a96c9896af6528694","tid":2491602,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fi0uvb3Yz3a6-NlMv3b02hy2BBs=/802x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CDGVMPHMSFHFPDCK4VFFSZPZBU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffi0uvb3Yz3a6-NlMv3b02hy2BBs%3D%2F802x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCDGVMPHMSFHFPDCK4VFFSZPZBU.jpeg&h=585199b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n匈牙利總理奧爾班與中國國家主席習近平。路透社<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n歐盟原訂在周一舉行的外長會上發表有關香港的聲明，旨在支持英國及美國維護香港人權，但由於匈牙利反對，故未能取得全部27個成員國同意。路透社引述一名資深歐盟外交官指：「匈牙利的論點是歐盟已經與中國有太多問題。」報道同時援引另一名資深外交官確認，匈牙利在這件事上持反對立場，一名歐盟官員更指，已從歐盟的批准程序中撤回聲明。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟上月22日就中國侵犯新疆維吾爾人的人權作出制裁，匈牙利當時不情願地支持歐盟制裁，但形容行動是「無意義」，更在歐盟決定制裁後幾日，正式接見訪匈的中國國防部長。匈牙利近年接受龐大中國投資，最近被揭發政府不惜向中國貸款，也要興建由中資企業負責的大學分校項目，過去曾與同樣接受很多中國資金的希臘出手阻止歐盟對中國事務發聲明。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210416/34QSDCA27FHBDDRVRBJSUM7TZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210416%2F34QSDCA27FHBDDRVRBJSUM7TZA%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=a129ea8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210416%2F34QSDCA27FHBDDRVRBJSUM7TZA%2F&h=53e0425e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210416/34QSDCA27FHBDDRVRBJSUM7TZA/</a>"},{"pid":"79d099b4940d3cc8800c3d54fbb6b82dcd9e088e","tid":2491602,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src